title: Cuisinart Deluxe Can Opener (CCO-50N) Demo Video
description: Style, convenience, and power come together in the Cuisinart electric can opener. With Chrome accents and elegant contours, it fits in nicely with other modern countertop appliances. The easy single-touch operation effortlessly opens and standard size can. The precision Power Cut® blade and strong magnetic lid holder are attached to the removable lever, which can be easily detached for quick cleanups.
